des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your Hamilton products. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download the “Hamilton Lite” app for your Smart phone and register an account;
(2) Configure your devices in the “Hamilton Lite” app and choose appropriate names for your devices;
(3) Download the Amazon "Alexa" app for Android or Apple from the app store then configure your Echo with the "Alexa" app;
(4) Search for the “Hamilton Lite” skill from the "Alexa" app in the skills category;
(5) Enable the “Hamilton Lite” skill, and you'll be navigated to the “Hamilton Lite” login page;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete device linking;
(7) Setup is complete. You can enjoy voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
